               <bibl>Pearl OM, Aegyptus 31, 223-224, 1951 -- SB VI 9231, 1 -- BL V, 111 (on line 1); BL VII, 204 (on line 6). - In lines 2-3, instead of me(nos) ; Paun[i hyp(er)], read: eph' he(meron) ; pent[e hyp(er)]. In line 4, read exath(uro) Pau(ni). (PH)</bibl>
            </listBibl>
